item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - SEVENTEEN - 10th Mini Album FML (QoBuz FLAC 16bits/44.1kHz)
item.description:
FML is the 10th mini album by SEVENTEEN. It was released on April 24, 2023 with "F*ck My Life" and "Super" serving as the album's double title tracks.
The physical album comes in four versions: A (Fallen, Misfit, Lost), B (Faded Mono Life), C (Fight for My Life), Carat and Kit.



Track list
"F*ck My Life" - 3:22
"Super (손오공)" - 3:20
"Fire" (Hip-Hop team) - 2:38
"I Don't Understand But I Love It" (Performance team) - 3:29
"Dust (먼지)" (Vocal team) - 2:45
"April Shower" - 3:32
